//twitter.com/UXAspects">@UXAspects</a>, open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/UXAspects/UXAspects/issues">GitHub</a>, or check our <a href="https://uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects/#/blog">blog</a> for more information!</p> </body></html>'},90351:t=>{t.exports='<html><head></head><body><p>UX Aspects 1.8.17 is available! Check out the documentation at <a href="https://uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects">uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects</a>.</p> <h4 id="bug-fixes-and-improvements">Bug Fixes and Improvements</h4> <ul> <li>(EL-3830) <a href="https://uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects/#/components/scrollbar#infinite-scroll">Infinite Scroll</a> - fixed an issue that prevents initial load when the provided promise completes very quickly.</li> </ul> <p>Any questions or feedback? Get in touch on Twitter <a href="https://twitter.com/UXAspects">@UXAspects</a>, open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/UXAspects/UXAspects/issues">GitHub</a>, or check our <a href="https://uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects/#/blog">blog</a> for more information!</p> </body></html>'},90494:t=>{t.exports='<html><head></head><body><p>UX Aspects 1.7.15 is available! Check out the documentation at <a href="https://uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects">uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects</a>.</p> <h4 id="bug-fixes-and-improvements">Bug Fixes and Improvements</h4> <ul> <li>(EL-3528) <a href="https://uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects/#/components/tables#column-resizing">Column Resizing</a> - horizontal scrollbar no longer unexpectedly appears when resizing; <code>undefined</code> or <code>null</code> value for <code>width</code> no longer causes the column width to be fixed.</li> <li>(EL-3529) <a href="https://uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects/#/components/wizard#marquee-wizard-ng1">Marquee Wizard (AngularJS)</a> - active step will be scrolled into view when the number of steps overflows the container.</li> <li>(EL-3540) <a href="https://uxaspects.github.io/UXAspects/#/components/date-time-picker#date-range-picker">Date Range Picker</